# 20.1 SEO Learning Roadmap

SEO ko ek din me nahi seekha ja sakta.

Professional SEO banne ke liye learning ko stages me divide karna best approach hai.

### Stage 1 – Beginner

Learn:

* SEO Basics
* Keywords
* Website Structure
* On-Page SEO
* URLs
* Images

Goal:

Understand how Google works.

---

### Stage 2 – Intermediate

Learn:

* Technical SEO
* Local SEO
* Content Marketing
* Mobile SEO
* Website Speed
* Backlinks

Goal:

Optimize real websites.

---

### Stage 3 – Advanced

Learn:

* Schema
* Google Search Console
* Google Analytics
* SEO Audit
* E-E-A-T
* AI SEO

Goal:

Handle complete SEO projects.

